{"tid":178420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網民熱話：大嘥鬼　水果店棄新鮮士多啤梨","createTime":"2017-03-29T13:56:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T20:59:08.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"098f49890e7bfd8395a159bce7542cd3c1c1549b","tid":178420,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:56:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170329/bkn-20170329210920395-0329_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170329%2Fbkn-20170329210920395-0329_00822_001.html&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=b50fb658\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170329/bkn-20170329210920395-0329_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170329/photo/bkn-20170329210920395-0329_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170329211651\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170329%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170329210920395-0329_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170329211651&h=45094991&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有公司棄置大量士多啤梨，被網民批評浪費。（Sarah Tong facebook 圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n從小已被教導要愛惜食物，不要吃剩食物、又不可隨便棄置，這個淺白的道理，大家又能否付諸實行呢？網民Sarah Tong日前在個人facebook上載了圖片貼文，圖中可見有大批士多啤梨被人棄置到垃圾桶內，發文者表示在中環元創方目睹事件：「啱啱親眼目擊成板新鮮士多啤梨揼落垃圾桶」，涉事為一間售賣水果的公司。發文者又斥職員「放工大晒？」<br />\n<br />\n事後該公司在facebook澄清指，因發霉等變質問題，士多啤梨不適宜食用，故揀選出來棄置。不少網民看見圖片後就質疑士多啤梨是否發霉，認為從圖中可見其色澤新鮮，如真的發霉，士多啤梨顏色會變暗變黑。又有網民指即使士多啤梨發霉，但仍有更佳的處理方法，例如用作烹調成果醬或環保酵素等。<br />\n<br />\n網民有話說<br />\nOlive Chu：我睇唔到佢邊忽壞，發霉樣 <br />\n<br />\nChu Hon Keung：除了扔掉，就沒有更好的做法了嗎？ <br />\n<br />\n鄭樂然：新鮮的，做環酵都心痛，點解會丟得落 <br />\n<br />\nAbey Cheng：就算真係霉晒都留畀我風晒做肥料，浪費，連回歸土地機會都無埋。"},{"pid":"012d1a8c48837bb3c479c271e35dc7292e91e41c","tid":178420,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:00:41.000Z","msg":"有乜問題"},{"pid":"7ee17ac9fd157e1e3c5fb19da34cdf2a7f93bc87","tid":178420,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:01:26.000Z","msg":"又關班環保撚事<br />\n咁得閒影相批鬥咪執翻嚟食囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce1756fa23ea3d57b1ff1e791b36cd927b86ac9","tid":178420,"uid":60238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:02:59.000Z","msg":"以香港人既閪格，如果知道鋪頭賣唔晒會派街坊既，實會日日喺門口捕撚住人地收工，甚至扮埋露宿者"},{"pid":"820eae4c07d2fc9a6257087ec34770b4b60533e1","tid":178420,"uid":47658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:03:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />扔左又話曬 食左過期野又話要告人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"588c2cc3b3bec8bc72036bc80457fc5c38f00586","tid":178420,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:05:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e99c180bc7e03d006d8cd8e5992a1fc369dd648e","tid":178420,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:06:01.000Z","msg":"咩撚野係「水果店」！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c5158fdaf09dc6ff75eea5931ee5e6c1fa6b70","tid":178420,"uid":69098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:08:10.000Z","msg":"發文者拍攝後離開現場<br />\n並立即回家於網上炮轟該公司行為<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想環保咪執番佢<br />\n拎番屋企洗乾淨再食囉<br />\n食唔晒咪派街坊<br />\n你唔講係垃圾筒執既邊有人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ce09149aacb66c22e9522694fa88c56921d5135","tid":178420,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:19:42.000Z","msg":"元創坊（PMQ）系咩人大家心照la"},{"pid":"7b8fc53ee1b2ad8662fd59ddb5fd796ce77665a2","tid":178420,"uid":31368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:21:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>元創坊（PMQ）<span style=\"color: red;\">系<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong></strong></span></span>咩人大家心照la</blockquote>"},{"pid":"ca26c59cc48c6f1cf4acb4681bef667f1b0ab01e","tid":178420,"uid":31368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:21:35.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - Sky_Croc )<br />\n字都唔識"},{"pid":"e38ffc75fe037293111ff9b2e92e4e4a20582308","tid":178420,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:28:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>元創坊（PMQ）系咩人大家心照la</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱啱星期日完左個以水果為主既巿集，佢果d士多啤莉應該係果日賣既西班牙士多啤莉。"},{"pid":"f1ea317830fb8c4eb16e28587f26efb297c3e380","tid":178420,"uid":2020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:35:52.000Z","msg":"點解要掉左去？<br />\n1. 慳運輸成本 生果呢d運得黎都爛哂啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.避免派比人做成法律責任 早幾年有單好心麵包店將賣唔哂麵包派比人 之後有人聲稱食左肚痛不適 告返間麵包鋪<br />\n<br />\n同埋 生果食唔食得唔係睇圖就睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df373a0b4e825f191a7c4109ff57d71973192c83","tid":178420,"uid":2020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:39:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170329/bkn-20170329210920395-0329_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170329%2Fbkn-20170329210920395-0329_00822_001.html&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=b50fb658\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170329/bkn-20170329210920395-0329_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170329/photo/bkn-20170329210920395-0329_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170329211651\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170329%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170329210920395-0329_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170329211651&h=45094991&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有公司棄置大量士多啤梨，被網民批評浪費。（Sarah Tong facebook 圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n從小已被教導要愛惜食物，不要吃剩食物、又不可隨便棄置，這個淺白的道理，大家又能否付諸實行呢？網民Sarah Tong日前在個人facebook上載了圖片貼文，圖中可見有大批士多啤梨被人棄置到垃圾桶內，發文者表示在中環元創方目睹事件：「啱啱親眼目擊成板新鮮士多啤梨揼落垃圾桶」，涉事為一間售賣水果的公司。發文者又斥職員「放工大晒？」<br />\n<br />\n事後該公司在facebook澄清指，因發霉等變質問題，士多啤梨不適宜食用，故揀選出來棄置。不少網民看見圖片後就質疑士多啤梨是否發霉，認為從圖中可見其色澤新鮮，如真的發霉，士多啤梨顏色會變暗變黑。又有網民指即使士多啤梨發霉，<span style=\"color: red;\">但仍有更佳的處理方法，例如用作烹調成果醬或環保酵素等。</span><br />\n<br />\n網民有話說<br />\nOlive Chu：我睇唔到佢邊忽壞，發霉樣 <br />\n<br />\nChu Hon Keung：除了扔掉，就沒有更好的做法了嗎？ <br />\n<br />\n鄭樂然：新鮮的，做環酵都心痛，點解會丟得落 <br />\n<br />\nAbey Cheng：就算真係霉晒都留畀我風晒做肥料，浪費，連回歸土地機會都無埋。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講就易 又唔見自己身體力行去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n理想還理想 現實d好唔好"},{"pid":"1b17046faecf2054e29408ff644017f56875b06f","tid":178420,"uid":45232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:40:35.000Z","msg":"佢未擺左落垃圾桶到等你執囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a945f5dead22bec59749d5fc92edccf21be3cb1a","tid":178420,"uid":36849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:45:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e3becf55e9dc0d246ffd0ac5d473259836a521a2","tid":178420,"uid":11977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:47:14.000Z","msg":"其實點解店主唔自己食左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"620c56177c51aefb6b3c1e04f31965a66afb5967","tid":178420,"uid":45591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:47:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢未擺左落垃圾桶到等你執囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n既然可以做肥料<br />\n咁佢咪執黎整囉"},{"pid":"fe9caabaf455a9f234a549521dce1c67d824e6cb","tid":178420,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:51:10.000Z","msg":"環保畜要搞就應該去搞呢d商家佬<br />\n而咪撚再搞d弱質市民"},{"pid":"c539c3088bd2e966585ee9a23f3b9b844bb9ed06","tid":178420,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T15:00:42.000Z","msg":"叫人做野ga 人永遠都唔會自己落手做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04362d3c5bba781e938d1529df1475120e6518e","tid":178420,"uid":11973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T18:23:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫人做野ga 人永遠都唔會自己落手做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知幾時開始班港豬養成咗呢啲戇鳩習慣<br />\n影張相擺上網就覺得自己做咗正義嘅化身<br />\n自我感覺良好<br />\n<br />\n你覺得人哋做錯咪兜口兜面話尻佢囉<br />\n你覺得人哋犯法咪報警囉<br />\n你純粹想發洩嘅返屋企捽碟打飛機咪得囉<br />\n吓吓擺上網叫人哋幫你公審家陣老撚奉嘅咩?<br />\n影張相就覺得自己完成使命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f975555bbff1a1d200f85e76e04dde604c418a3","tid":178420,"uid":65406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T18:26:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實點解店主唔自己食左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食得咩都糖尿"},{"pid":"b6569511ef07dbd5f7e9eb73c847927018e52b85","tid":178420,"uid":17352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T18:32:09.000Z","msg":"環保撚係特別on9"},{"pid":"10418888c0fc4e2c7b26e77dc6ef864bc6542f6c","tid":178420,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T18:45:19.000Z","msg":"又有網民指即使士多啤梨發霉，但仍有更佳的處理方法，例如用作烹調成果醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n癡線"},{"pid":"cbeccd845a10ce4bda92c3b41832658a53cb050e","tid":178420,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T18:46:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以香港人既閪格，如果知道鋪頭賣唔晒會派街坊既，實會日日喺門口捕撚住人地收工，甚至扮埋露宿者</blockquote><br />\n呢樣又真係有可能 唔買 係度等人派"}]}